#. Description of the theme
#: style.css
msgid "Packers Logistic is a purpose-driven theme tailored for transportation, cargo, and relocation businesses that require a structured and functional website. It is well-suited for logistics companies, moving services, freight agencies, courier services, and warehouse operations aiming to present their offerings with clarity. The layout is designed to highlight essential elements such as service listings, shipment tracking sections, quote request forms, and contact information without unnecessary clutter. Built with performance in mind, the theme supports fast loading and integrates smoothly with essential plugins, making it reliable for shipping companies and supply chain businesses. It includes flexible customization options, organized typography, and intuitive navigation to help users align the website with their brand identity. Packers Logistic provides a practical framework for displaying services, operational areas, pricing details, and logistics solutions in a clean and accessible format."
msgstr ""

